1
00:00:10,933.3329999999987 --> 206:08:30,933.3329999446869
The travelers laid the soaked scrolls on some rocks.

2
206:10:10,933.3329999446869 --> 304:56:50,933.3329999446869
"The sun will dry them out," said Wukong.

3
304:58:30,933.3329999446869 --> 367:38:30,933.3329999446869
[g@The Tang Monk moaned.

4
367:40:10,933.3329999446869 --> 437:26:50,933.3329999446869
"What if they're ruined?"@g]

5
437:28:30,933.3329999446869 --> 536:55:10,933.3329999446869
He sat down and put his head in his hands.

6
536:56:50,933.3329999446869 --> 672:20:10,933.3330001831055
"I wish I'd remembered to ask Buddha the turtle's question!"

7
672:21:50,933.3330001831055 --> 740:50:10,933.3330001831055
[g@Bajie snorted.

8
740:51:50,933.3330001831055 --> 825:13:30,933.3330001831055
"Who cares if you forgot the turtle's question?@g]

9
825:15:10,933.3330001831055 --> 942:36:50,933.3330001831055
