10
942:38:30,933.3330001831055 --> 1051:05:10,933.3330001831055
"Dumping us in the water was rude," Wujing agreed.

11
1051:06:50,933.3330001831055 --> 1121:43:30,933.3330001831055
Bajie sighed.

12
1121:45:10,933.3330001831055 --> 1257:06:50,933.3330001831055
"The journey back east is becoming just as difficult as the journey west."

13
1257:08:30,933.3330001831055 --> 1324:13:30,933.3330001831055
"Hello!" cried a voice.

14
1324:15:10,933.3330001831055 --> 1462:33:30,933.3330001831055
The travelers turned and saw a man hurrying toward them.

15
1462:35:10,933.3330001831055 --> 1526:51:50,933.3330001831055
[g@"Chen," said the Tang Monk.

16
1526:53:30,933.3330001831055 --> 1599:15:10,933.3330001831055
He grasped the man's hands.@g]

17
1599:16:50,933.3330001831055 --> 1669:00:10,933.3330001831055
"It's good to see you again."

18
1669:01:50,933.3330001831055 --> 1767:08:30,933.3330001831055
"It's good to see all of you." Chen smiled.

19
1767:10:10,933.3330001831055 --> 1848:58:30,933.3330001831055
"Did you reach the Western Paradise?"

20
1849:00:10,933.3330001831055 --> 1911:36:50,933.3330001831055
"Yes," said the Tang Monk.

21
1911:38:30,933.3330001831055 --> 1965:50:10,933.3330001831055
[g@"It was magnificent!

22
1965:51:50,933.3330001831055 --> 2046:06:50,933.3330001831055
