24
2199:41:50,933.3330001831055 --> 2328:36:50,933.3330001831055
"Are those the True Scriptures?" he whispered.

25
2328:38:30,933.3330001831055 --> 2385:21:50,933.3330001831055
[g@"Yes," said the monk.

26
2385:23:30,933.3330001831055 --> 2522:26:50,933.3330001831055
"But as you can see, they got wet."@g]

27
2522:28:30,933.3330001831055 --> 2683:43:30,933.3330001831055
"A giant turtle dumped us in the river," added Bajie with a sigh.

28
2683:45:10,933.3330001831055 --> 2757:16:50,933.3330001831055
"Please come with me," said Chen.

29
2757:18:30,933.3330001831055 --> 2840:10:10,933.3330001831055
"You can dry the True Scriptures by my fire.

30
2840:11:50,933.3330001831055 --> 2973:40:10,933.3330001831055
Everyone in the village will be excited to see [n@the travelers who met Buddha."

31
2973:41:50,933.3330001831055 --> 3084:31:50,933.3330001831055
