32
3084:33:30,933.3330001831055 --> 3167:20:10,933.3330001831055
"I'll help you," said Bajie.

33
3167:21:50,933.3330001831055 --> 3259:13:30,933.3330001831055
[g@The pig grabbed a scroll and pulled.

34
3259:15:10,933.3330001831055 --> 3335:48:30,933.3330001831055
