55
5363:26:50,933.3330001831055 --> 5595:43:30,933.3330001831055
They will also teach the people that nothing needs to be perfect."

56
5595:45:10,933.3330001831055 --> 5821:01:50,933.3330001831055
The travelers finished gathering the scrolls [n@and followed Chen back to the village.

57
5821:03:30,933.3330001831055 --> 5934:48:30,933.3330001831055
