58
5934:50:10,933.3330001831055 --> 6013:11:50,933.3330001831055
"Welcome back!" called a woman.

59
6013:13:30,933.3330001831055 --> 6137:36:50,933.3330001831055
"It's wonderful to see you all again!" shouted an old man.

60
6137:38:30,933.3330001831055 --> 6344:05:10,933.3330001831055
Soon a crowd was following the Tang Monk [n@and his companions to Chen's house.

61
6344:06:50,933.3330001831055 --> 6463:40:10,933.3330001831055
