62
6463:41:50,933.3330001831055 --> 6599:58:30,933.3330001831055
Later that night Wukong and the Tang Monk sat, talking.

63
6600:00:10,933.3330001831055 --> 6672:28:30,933.3330001831055
"We must leave soon," said the monk.

64
6672:30:10,933.3330001831055 --> 6767:26:50,933.3330001831055
"The villagers will want to see the True Scriptures.

65
6767:28:30,933.3330001831055 --> 6861:58:30,933.3330001831055
They'll become jealous that we have them."

66
6862:00:10,933.3330001831055 --> 6935:41:50,933.3330001831055
"I agree," said Wukong.

67
6935:43:30,933.3330001831055 --> 7088:46:50,933.3330001831055
He remembered the priest who'd tried to kill [n@the Tang Monk and steal the robe.

68
7088:48:30,933.3330001831055 --> 7218:08:30,933.3330001831055
