70
7338:23:30,933.3330001831055 --> 7458:13:30,933.3330001831055
The group sneaked out of Chen's house and headed east.

71
7458:15:10,933.3330001831055 --> 7608:55:10,933.3330001831055
It was dark, but the light from the full moon lit up the road.

72
7608:56:50,933.3330001831055 --> 7724:40:10,933.3330001831055
Suddenly the guard from the Thunderclap Monastery appeared.

73
7724:41:50,933.3330001831055 --> 7824:33:30,933.3330001831055
[g@"Congratulations!" said the guard.

74
7824:35:10,933.3330001831055 --> 7932:03:30,933.3330001831055
"You have faced one hundred challenges."@g]

75
7932:05:10,933.3330001831055 --> 8037:10:10,933.3330001831055
[g@"Whew." The monk sighed with relief.

76
8037:11:50,933.3330001831055 --> 8123:51:50,933.3330001831055
"I will become a buddha at last."@g]

77
8123:53:30,933.3330001831055 --> 8208:10:10,933.3330001831055
[g@The guard recited a spell.

78
8208:11:50,933.3330001831055 --> 8482:45:10,933.3330001831055
Once again the travelers flew toward the East.@g]

